Global Variable# NSMetadataItemFSCreationDateKey

iOS 5.0+iPadOS 5.0+Mac Catalyst 13.1+macOS 10.7+tvOS 9.0+visionOS 1.0+watchOS 2.0+

```
let NSMetadataItemFSCreationDateKey: String
```

## [Discussion](/documentation/Foundation/NSMetadataItemFSCreationDateKey#Discussion)

The value is an [`NSDate`](/documentation/foundation/nsdate) object that contains the date and time that the file was created.
